  "text": "GPC3-derived peptide vaccine in a phase I trial for advanced HCC patients. [CITATION_1] We are currently conducting a phase II trial with a GPC3-derived peptide vaccine in ovarian CCC patients (UMIN-CTR: 000003696).",
